<html class="h-100" lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Blue Ball Machine</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/cookie.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/other.css">
    <link rel="preload" as="style" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="preload" as="style" href="/static/other.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/media/favicon/blueball.png">
    <meta property="og:image" content="/media/favicon/blueball.png">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="/media/favicon/blueball.png">
    <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#ffffff">
    <link rel="manifest" href="/media/favicon/site.webmanifest">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="title" content="Blue Ball Machine">
    <meta name="description" content="Blue Ball Machine; creates blue balls.">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#1e2ffc">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
    <meta name="twitter:site" content="@ATProductsLLC">
    <meta name="twitter:creator" content="@ATProductsLLC">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Blue Ball Machine">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Blue Ball Machine; creates blue balls.">
    <meta name="author" content="Alex Toucan">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Blue Ball Machine">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Blue Ball Machine; creates blue balls.">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <style>
      body {
        background: url(/media/images/image.gif);
      }
    </style>

    <style>
      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0; }
        to { opacity: 1; }
      }

      @keyframes fadeOut {
        from { opacity: 1; }
        to { opacity: 0; }
      }

      .fade-in {
        animation: fadeIn 1s forwards;
      }

      .fade-out {
        animation: fadeOut 1s forwards;
      }

      .notification-container {
        padding-right: 4rem !important;
        display: none;
      }

      .notification-close-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.5rem;
        right: 0.5rem;
      }

      @media (min-width: 480.98px) {
          .arrow {
              margin-left: 21.75rem !important;
          }
          .pb-custom-2 {
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
          }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480.98px) {
          .notification-container, .arrow {
              position: sticky !important;
              top: 100% !important;
              white-space: normal !important;
          }
          .arrow {
              height: 100%;
              margin-bottom: 0 !important;
          }
          .notification-content {
            display: flex
          }
      }

      @media (min-width: 767.98px) {
        .hero-main {
          background-image: url(/media/images/hero.webp) !important;
          background-size: cover !important;
          background-position: center center !important;
          background-repeat: no-repeat !important;
          filter: drop-shadow(2px 4px 6px black);
        }
      }

      .hero-main {
        background: initial;
      }

      .tab {
        text-indent: 2rem;
      }

      @media (min-width: 767.98px) {
        .information-btn {
          margin-bottom: calc(1rem * 4 + 42px) !important;
        }
      }
    </style>

    <script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@4.0.0-beta/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="h-100">

    <div class="position-fixed bottom-0 end-0 me-3" style="margin-bottom: calc(1rem * 2 + 42px);" id="information-btn">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary py-2 d-flex align-items-center shadow-lg" id="bd-information" type="button" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#informationModal">
        <span>
          <i class="my-1 bi bi-info"></i>
        </span>
        <span class="visually-hidden" id="bd-information-text">Toggle information modal</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-dark rounded-2 position-fixed bottom-0 end-0 m-2 pt-3 ps-3 pb-2 text-light shadow-lg notification-container" id="audio-notification" data-bs-theme="dark">
      <button type="button" class="btn-close notification-close-btn p-3" aria-label="Close" id="close-notification"></button>
      <div class="notification-content">
        <p class="h4 pb-4 pb-custom-2 pb-md-0">There is audio that could be played!</p>
        <i class="h1 bi bi-arrow-right arrow"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="position-fixed bottom-0 end-0 me-3" style="margin-bottom: calc(1rem * 5.6 + 42px);" id="preset-btn">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary py-2 d-flex align-items-center shadow-lg" id="bd-presets" type="button" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#presetModal">
        <span>
          <i class="my-1 bi bi-palette-fill"></i>
        </span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Open presets</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="modal fade" id="presetModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="presetModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content bg-dark text-light">

          <div class="modal-header">
            <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="presetModalLabel">Blue Ball Machine Presets</h1>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
          </div>

          <div class="modal-body">

            <h5 class="mb-3">Background Themes</h5>
            <div class="row g-3">

              <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                <div class="card bg-secondary text-light preset-bg preset-linked" 
                    data-bg="/media/images/image.gif" 
                    data-music="/media/images/sound.mp3"
                    data-loop="true">
                  <img src="/media/images/image.gif" class="card-img-top object-fit-cover" height="70px">
                  <div class="card-body p-2 text-center"><small>Classic Machine</small></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                <div class="card bg-secondary text-light preset-bg preset-linked" 
                    data-bg="/media/images/blueballtragedy.gif"
                    data-music="/media/images/blueballtragedy.mp3"
                    data-loop="false">
                  <img src="/media/images/blueballtragedy.gif" class="card-img-top object-fit-cover" height="70px">
                  <div class="card-body p-2 text-center"><small>Blue Ball Tragedy</small></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                <div class="card bg-secondary text-light preset-bg preset-linked" 
                    data-bg="/media/images/tiger.gif"
                    data-music="/media/images/tiger.mp3"
                    data-loop="true">
                  <img src="/media/images/tiger.gif" class="card-img-top object-fit-cover" height="70px">
                  <div class="card-body p-2 text-center"><small>Tiger Handheld</small></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                <div class="card bg-secondary text-light preset-bg preset-linked" 
                    data-bg="/media/images/lazy.gif"
                    data-music="/media/images/sound.mp3"
                    data-loop="true">
                  <img src="/media/images/lazy.gif" class="card-img-top object-fit-cover" height="70px">
                  <div class="card-body p-2 text-center"><small>Lazy Mode</small></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                <div class="card bg-secondary text-light preset-bg preset-linked" 
                    data-bg="/media/images/jones.gif"
                    data-music="/media/images/sound.mp3"
                    data-loop="true">
                  <img src="/media/images/jones.gif" class="card-img-top object-fit-cover" height="70px">
                  <div class="card-body p-2 text-center"><small>Indiana Jones</small></div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>

            <hr class="my-4">

            <h5 class="mb-3">Music Remixes</h5>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">

              <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-light d-flex justify-content-between align-items-between preset-music" data-music="/media/images/sound.mp3">
                <span>Original Soundtrack</span>
                <div>
                  <button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm preview-btn">Preview</button>
                  <button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm apply-music-btn ms-2">Apply</button>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-light d-flex justify-content-between align-items-between preset-music" data-music="/media/images/rock.mp3">
                <span>Rock Version</span>
                <div>
                  <button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm preview-btn">Preview</button>
                  <button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm apply-music-btn ms-2">Apply</button>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-light d-flex justify-content-between align-items-between preset-music" data-music="/media/images/tiger.mp3">
                <span>Tiger Handheld Version</span>
                <div>
                  <button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm preview-btn">Preview</button>
                  <button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm apply-music-btn ms-2">Apply</button>
                </div>
              </li>

            </ul>

          </div>

          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="applyPresetBtn">Apply Preset</button>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="modal fade" id="informationModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="informationModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="informationModalLabel">Information & Credits</h1>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <div class="hero hero-main p-md-4 rounded-2 mb-3">
              <div class="bg-dark p-2 rounded-2 d-grid mx-auto" style="width: 217px;filter: drop-shadow(2px 4px 6px black);">
                <span class="text-center fw-bold fs-4 text-white mb-2">Made by:</span>
                <a class="btn btn-dark py-2" type="button" href="https://atproducts.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <img alt="AT Products LLC" src="https://atproducts.xyz/media/images/longwhite.png" width="175px">
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h2>Credits</h2>
            <p class="mb-1"><b>Author:</b> <a href="https://portfolio.atproducts.xyz">Alex Toucan</a></p>
            <p class="mb-1"><b>Original Creators:</b> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20060426005946/http://ytmnd.com/users/profile/40320">Earthbounder</a> and <a href="https://ytmnd.com/users/benjabean1">benjabean1</a></p>
            <p class="mb-1"><b>Audio:</b> Breakfast Machine (From "Pee Wee's Big Adventure")</p>
            <p class="mb-1"><b>Foreground:</b> Unknown but first appeared on <a href="https://ytmnd.com/">YTMND</a>.</p>
            <p class="mb-1"><b>Scripter:</b> <a href="https://portfolio.atproducts.xyz">Alex Toucan</a></p>
            <p><b>Release Date:</b> April 7th, 2025</p>
            <h2>History</h2>
            <div class="text-justify">
              <p class="tab">The Blue Ball Machine first appeared on <a href="http://blueballfixed.ytmnd.com/">YTMND</a> in 2005, a community platform where "You're the Man Now, Dog" users create and share meme based web pages. Andorion originally developed the concept, designing a template and sample tiles while inviting community contributions. Hundreds of participants from the Something Awful forums subsequently created the individual images.</p>
              <p class="tab">Immediately after its creation, the site gained popularity on YTMND, which resulted in various spinoffs, and its own <a href="https://wiki.ytmnd.com/Blue_Ball_Machine">wiki page</a>. The site was created or at least owned by <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20060426005946/http://ytmnd.com/users/profile/40320">the account of Earthbounder</a>. The site would later stop working, according to archives around 2009.</p>
              <p class="tab">The site would later be brought to <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20121231200144/http://www.haneke.net/">haneke.net</a> from mid-2008, to its demise in early 2017. The site used to be a <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20030320100006/http://haneke.net/">German "Internetportal"</a> in 2003, and <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20031206074816/http://www.haneke.net/#">was a red button that opened a pop-up with the text "HANEKE"</a> later that same year. The site later become the <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20080420084457/http://www.haneke.net/"></a>Blue Ball Machine that we all know and love from early-mid 2008</a>.</p>
              <p class="tab">The site exploded in popularity from late 2012, which even appeared on the <a href="https://theuselessweb.com/">The Useless Web</a> at one point, according to <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20141103194304/http://www.theuselessweb.com/js/uselessweb.js">its list from 2013-2014</a>. The site sadly disappeared in mid-2017. The site is now a <a href="http://www.haneke.net/">nest box live camera</a> from 2021, and still exists in 2025.</p>
              <p class="tab">However, <a href="http://blueballfixed.ytmnd.com/">the YTMND site would be revived</a> in mid-2019, as they switched from Flash to HTML5, which appears to now be maintained <a href="https://ytmnd.com/users/benjabean1">by a user called benjabean1</a>. The site reads that the GIF's origin is "... unknown, but it has been used on many YTMNDs before." And the sound is from "Pee Wee's Big Adventure".</p>
            </div>
            <h2>Spin-offs</h2> 
              <p>These spin-offs can also be found on the <i class="bi bi-palette-fill"></i> button.</p>
              <ul>
                <li><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20070118052006/http://blueballhandheld.ytmnd.com/">Blue Ball Tiger Handheld</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://blueballtragedy.ytmnd.com/">Tragedy at the Blue Ball Factory!</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://indyblueballs.ytmnd.com/">Indiana Jones Can't Stop The Blue Ball Machine</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://blueballlazy.ytmnd.com/">Blue Ball Machine (Lazy version)</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://metalblueballfactory.ytmnd.com/">Blue Ball Tiger Handheld</a></li>

              </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="position-fixed bottom-0 end-0 mb-3 me-3">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary py-2 d-flex align-items-center shadow-lg" id="bd-audio" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span class="audio-icon-active">
          <i class="my-1 bi bi-volume-mute-fill"></i>
        </span>
        <span class="visually-hidden" id="bd-audio-text">Toggle audio</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  
    <script is:inline src="/static/blue.js"></script>

    <script is:inline src="/static/message.js"></script>
    

  </body>
</html>
